{"tid":1416355,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦永遠比我地走得更前","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:21:32.000Z","uid":207762,"like":76,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"58cb2b1da12c22d6df0ee001e84d81a4c2576961","tid":1416355,"uid":207762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"在槍林彈雨中，親眼目睹鮮血灑在街頭，聽見四周的哀嚎吶喊，定必使你們悲憤不已<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。但我懇請你們<span style=\"color: red;\">不要被仇恨支配自己</span>，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n我時常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，<span style=\"color: green;\">而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己</span>，改變想法，認同自己的方向<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n我想，我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日見倒太多失控場面，大家都想贏，但物極必反，前線必須保持理智，贏得漂亮。<br />\n<br />\n利申：永不割蓆"},{"pid":"9e5799ec0fd937a3828e675c61ebf018f2e00adf","tid":1416355,"uid":207762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d212fea2200a5c47656b8ef8658571225a9e51e","tid":1416355,"uid":207762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29a5110700a638848ad37b58cdbdae00083f9624","tid":1416355,"uid":207762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dad6838d7f74121aac7e67f4b12d33e841d5a98e","tid":1416355,"uid":207762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:00:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50e5b722b015d6620abf629356aba8dd002bd7b1","tid":1416355,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f47c8660184124600e6cbea49ebc4876a0ef5198","tid":1416355,"uid":152440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:02:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d0e4e329cfef1fc9df76a44a8fc26e5db55158d","tid":1416355,"uid":207762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"